{
  "texts": [
    "We predicted the R e for all IDRs and used the s.d.",
    "of these predicted R e values to quantify the conservation of IDR dimensions; a larger s.d.",
    "implies a lack of conservation, whereas a smaller s.d.",
    "implies that the end-to-end distance is less variable.",
    "We quantified homolog sequence divergence using two approaches: by computing the variation of IDR sequence lengths and by scoring the sequence similarities from the multiple sequence alignment (Methods)."
  ]
}